author: hlship
msg: Be careful about which inner classes are added to the load list
Without the checks, inner classes (such as java.util.Map$Entry) could be added as loaded by the reloading class loader, rather than delegated to the parent class loader

msg: TAP5-1650: Change the service/object reloader to use Plastic, not Javassist

author: hlship
msg: TAP-1650: Remove extra synchronization that is (probably) not needed
